Aleksandra Delcheva (Bulgarian: Александра Делчева, amụrụ n April 11, 1987) bụ onye Bulgaria na egwu volleyball na basketball, na-egwu dị ka onye etiti.
Delcheva malitere ọrụ basketball ya na ụlọ ọrụ WBC Slavia Sofia dị na Hungary wee kpọọ ebe ahụ n'etiti 2009 na 2012 (egwuregwu 68, na-eme isi 532)
N'ime oge ikpeazụ ya, 2011–12, ọ gbara na Slavia (Nkewa A), gbara egwuregwu 24 wee nwee 8.5ppg na 7.3rpg
Mgbe oge ahụ gasịrị, ọ kwagara Czech Republic ka ya na DSK Basketball Karlin gwuo oge (egwuregwu 25, na-eme isi 82)
Otu afọ ka e mesịrị, ọ kwagara Ịtali wee soro Libertas Trogylos Basket gwuo egwu na Njikọ Ịtali (16 egwuregwu, na-eme isi 66)
N'ime egwuregwu 13 A1 ọ gbagoro 4.5ppg na 7.4rpg
Ahọpụtara Delcheva ka ọ bụrụ egwuregwu egwuregwu All-Star nke Italian League na 2014.
Delcheva nọchitere anya Bulgaria na otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Bulgaria kemgbe afọ 2011, gụnyere EuroBasket Ntozu ụmụ nwanyị 2013.
